==Hebrew==
===Etymology===
A primitive root.

===Pronunciation===
/ tsâvâh / tsaw-vaw'

===Verb===
<div><font size="15">צוה</font> (tsaváh)</div>

# (intensively) to constitute, enjoin: - appoint, (for-) bid. (give a) charge, (give a, give in, send with) command (-er, ment), send a messenger, put, (set) in order.

